data.description: Discover the charm of this meticulously maintained RARE END unit condo at Tequesta Gardens, where natural light fills every corner, and boasts an extra out side seating area exclusive to end units! AC unit (2021) hot water heater (2018). Nestled in Tequesta, the condo offers tranquility with easy access  to fine dining, and top-rated medical care. Some of which are with in walking distance. Amenities like pools, a library, putting green, outside grilling area and more!  Additionally, it comes fully furnished if the new buyer would like, ensuring a seamless transition into this inviting and well-appointed home perfect for snowbirds seeking a warm and welcoming retreat.
